name: Outerspace Cafe
description:
You're just chilling in your cafe and BAM! A small alien child comes to bug you! It's up to you to decide her fate into the alien she grows up to be! 

This visual novel has 4 endings, a netural ending, a bad ending, a good ending, and a true ending!

This was a project made for school with a rushed deadline and my first full game so don't expect much lol.
